    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Please note that code like this produces different results with and without optimization. Perhaps another reason to remove `pc()`\r\n\r\n```\r\npragma solidity >= 0.0.0;\r\ncontract C {\r\n        function test() public returns (int)\r\n        {\r\n                int8 v0 = int8(0xdc4c7fbf8ec49ab53bc225a482aad76de9d21c98cbf2a163c351192dfaec2e05);\r\n                assembly {\r\n                        v0 := pc()\r\n                }\r\n                return int(v0);\r\n        }\r\n}\r\n```",
